  "title": "Guest Room Ambassador (Linen Attendant)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position summary statement:</strong><br /><br />Linen Room - Responsibilities: Maintain clean Linen Room, daily linen count/distribution, wash towels, record condemned linens, and organize staff uniforms by name</p><p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Handle guest laundry and HOD/staff laundry.</li><li>Distribution of Fresh  Face towel to Room Attendant </li><li>Perform daily linen count and distribution of fresh linens.</li><li>Ensure the linen chute is emptied before the end of the shift.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of Linen Room.</li><li>Wash Face Towel, Gym Towel, Sofa Cover in house.</li><li>Responsible for upkeep of washer and dryer in bin center</li><li>Counting and recording condemned linens</li><li>Count the soiled uniforms and, after receiving clean uniforms, organize the shirts and pants according to each staff member's name</li><li>Carry out assigned tasks by Guest Room Team Leader and ensure that job is carried out as instructed.</li><li>Inform Guest Room Team Leader of any related job deficiencies and ensure that problems are rectified before the end of the shift.</li><li>Prioritize needs of job to be done during the shift.</li><li>Follow Housekeeping procedures and emergency procedures on health and safety for employee and guests.</li><li>Report any damages to Guest Room Team Leader discovered in working areas.</li></ul>",
